---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="History — Saving South Street">
  <section class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-900">History</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-stone-700">
      A narrative history of South Street's evolution across the 20th and early 21st centuries — from streetcar
      commercial corridor through urban renewal, the South Street Renaissance, and the present day. The format
      of this page (long-form chapter, interactive timeline, or scroll-driven narrative) is still being decided.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
